{"tid":1591452,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"922沙田示威3男女　被控參與暴動罪","createTime":"2019-09-24T07:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T11:07:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce90baf005ddf8b6e91103fc592a74c60e3977a","tid":1591452,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:04:35.000Z","msg":"周日（22日）下午，網民發起到沙田連城廣場及新城市廣場築流動人鏈及罷買活動，有示威者在源禾路設置路障，並縱火焚燒雜物。警方於當日下午在源禾路拘捕2男1女，年齡介乎23歲至42歲，涉嫌「非法集結」。新界南總區重案組經進一步調查及徵詢法律意見後，3名被捕男女已各被暫控一項「參與暴動」，當中23歲姓周被捕男子，同時被暫控一項「藏有攻擊性武器」及「阻礙警務人員執行職務」。案件於今日（24日）下午在沙田裁判法院提堂。"},{"pid":"95b4c131b4e7a55ab21f16cc4ea77415a76156fa","tid":1591452,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:04:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190924/bkn-20190924134938943-0924_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190924%2Fbkn-20190924134938943-0924_00822_001.html&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=108ec9c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190924/bkn-20190924134938943-0924_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fc10e2c0115a57ee69a5d42fc00cbab7e31b7a05","tid":1591452,"uid":93141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:05:31.000Z","msg":"殺人係要填命既，贊唔贊成？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1591174/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1591174/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a64afcf3dd0c9f73f1f77a6e8a9baf018be25319","tid":1591452,"uid":5893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c828611673f31c0c2671f55bfd59e31bced050ab","tid":1591452,"uid":164585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225d44d8d831212e2dfa07ccb539f8f483930820","tid":1591452,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:08:14.000Z","msg":"唔會告得入"},{"pid":"d0d59bfa96039af8666c0dc2a69a8b32b4e2e14c","tid":1591452,"uid":321345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:13:41.000Z","msg":"其中一條仔係為左救女俾狗咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95058ce09ecaea82c72b15022e4e6fd2280e642f","tid":1591452,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Q1RNV6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Q1RNV6.jpg&h=227effc3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef72f2f5c953165b1ffcf2119634e4e4c2a5a776","tid":1591452,"uid":62314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:17:15.000Z","msg":"暫控？不如你暫控謀殺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f757c0ee44420195a1f5c75c2d0b4b83359c56d","tid":1591452,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:18:16.000Z","msg":"一定告唔入"},{"pid":"fe4f74cf76d106f14b6e3d7ba27a612c85c34786","tid":1591452,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:18:24.000Z","msg":"黑警仆街死"},{"pid":"5961cf24af2e624fc744fa071968496e55a04fd3","tid":1591452,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:18:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"473408198f949bd288331a35f179d4a6ca1a1e60","tid":1591452,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:43:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cf061f0ca3d2438eb37afbfe7923a8ce6b228f6","tid":1591452,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:07:49.000Z","msg":"3名被告依次為售貨員陳樂兒（24歲）、工程師周錦威（23歲）及地產區域經理黃溢霖（43歲），他們同被控一項暴動罪，指3被告於9月22日在沙田好運中心外，連同其他身分不詳人士參與暴動。周錦威另被控在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器及阻差辦公兩罪，指他在同時同地管有鐵鎚、鉗及螺絲批，以及阻礙高級督察林佩武執行職務。<br />\n<br />\n據知，當日下午約5時30分有示威者在好運中心對開，以小巴路牌、垃圾桶等雜物設置路障，並燃起火種。近6時，警方進行清場，拘捕了陳樂兒，而周錦威則因意圖拉走陳時一同被捕，警方在其身上搜出鐵鎚。當日兩人曾分別手持鐵鎚，與其他示威者聚集在一起，而黃溢霖則有搬鐵馬。<br />\n<br />\n另外21歲跟車工人羅敏聰被控一項侮辱國旗罪，指他在新城市廣場及沙田大會堂一帶，公開及故意以毀損、塗劃、玷污、踐踏的方式侮辱國旗。據了解，被告當日曾踐踏國旗，並將國旗塞進垃圾桶再推落噴水池，其後才有人撈起國旗並將之丟入城門河中。<br />\n<br />\n4人均准以1萬元保釋外出，須遵守晚10朝6的宵禁令及不可離港，被控暴動3被告不可踏入好運中心，3人案件押後至11月26日再訊，以待警方作進一步調查；而羅敏聰則不可踏足沙田新城市廣場100米範圍內，其案件押後至10月15日，以待辯方提供法律意見予被告。"},{"pid":"680b0c9d9255b19fc59e0c6cc136516513e578c4","tid":1591452,"uid":260659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:09:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">策略post</span></span><br />\n共產黨要香港人「民眾鬥民眾」我地就策動「popo鬥popo/公安/解放軍」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1591458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1591458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n入黎俾d意見"},{"pid":"a61a1ca937537c161b068cccf2fc647859a99448","tid":1591452,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"680b0c9d9255b19fc59e0c6cc136516513e578c4","tid":1591452,"uid":260659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:09:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">策略post</span></span><br />\n共產黨要香港人「民眾鬥民眾」我地就策動「popo鬥popo/公安/解放軍」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1591458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1591458</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n入黎俾d意見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:13:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de5ebce0d7c88e1805c6c8daeb0f4c9899a51dc","tid":1591452,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ce90baf005ddf8b6e91103fc592a74c60e3977a","tid":1591452,"uid":240362,"like":